      <title>由于太阳能行业陷入危机，欧洲因中国进口陷入困境</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/with-solar-industry-crisis-europe-bind-over-chinese-imports-2024-02-06/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲的绿色能源转型陷入进退两难的境地。大量廉价的中国太阳能电池板进口正在推动太阳能安装量创历史新高。但同样的进口正在压垮欧洲为数不多的本地太阳能制造商。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/with-solar-industry-crisis-europe-bind-over-chinese-imports-2024-02-06/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 12:41:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
